snippet.title: Sanwal Yaar Piya | Teaser 1 | Ft. Feroze Khan, Durefishan Saleem, Ahmed Ali Akbar | Drama Bazar
snippet.description:
ISHQ MAI KHAIRAAT NAHI HOTI
When fate ties three lives together, love lights the way, but struggles darken the path, and sacrifice becomes their only choice. 7th Sky Entertainment proudly presents the highly anticipated mega drama serial Sanwal Yaar Piya, starring the blockbuster trio Feroze Khan, Durefishan Saleem, and Ahmed Ali Akbar.

#SanwalYaarPiya is coming soon only on Drama Bazar

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Danish Nawaz

snippet.description:
Baaghi 4 Remake - Tiger Shroff Trailer Reaction By Deeksha Sharma. Baaghi 4 Trailer presented Tiger Shroff like never before in Hard Hitting Action Scenes with Unexpected Sanjay Dutt Villain Character & Harnaaz Sandhu as Mysterious lover but Sonam Bajwa is still a mystery. Expanding upon the world created by Danny Boyle and Alex Garland in 28 Years Later but turning that world on its head - Nia DaCosta directs 28 Years Later: The Bone Temple. In a continuation of the epic story, Dr. Kelson (Ralph Fiennes) finds himself in a shocking new relationship - with consequences that could change the world as they know it - and Spike's (Alfie Williams) encounter with Jimmy Crystal (Jack O'Connell) becomes a nightmare he can't escape. In the world of The Bone Temple, the infected are no longer the greatest threat to survival - the inhumanity of the survivors can be stranger and more terrifying.

Amazon MGM Studios India has announced its theatrical movie Nishaanchi, which is set to premiere on September 19. Directed by Anurag Kashyap, this raw and gritty theatrical crime drama is produced by Ajay Rai and Ranjan Singh under the banner of Jar Pictures in association with Flip Films. Nishaanchi marks the powerful acting debut of Aaishvary Thackeray who stars alongside Vedika Pinto, Monika Panwar, Mohammed Zeeshan Ayyub and Kumud Mishra in pivotal roles. Crafted for the big screen, Nishaanchi delivers a gripping, cinematic experience that delves into the complex lives of two brothers who walk starkly different paths, uncovering how their choices shape their destinies.

Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth in lead roles, this soulful track is composed by none other than Anirudh Ravichander, known for his chart-topping melodies and heart-touching compositions. Thangapoovey blends emotion with melody, capturing the essence of love and longing with poetic visuals and heartfelt lyrics.

With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudhâ€™s music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. As anticipation builds for Madharaasi, this song sets the perfect tone, offering a glimpse into the filmâ€™s emotional landscape.

snippet.title: TROPHIES ARE GONE?!
snippet.description:
Learn everything about the biggest matchmaking change in Clash of Clans history and what it means for you.
This change is coming with our next big update, but we wanted to give you a heads up so you can prepare.
For the first time ever, you will be able to choose how you want to Clash. Whether you're looking for competitive battles or a more relaxed way to play, this change gives you the freedom to pick the experience that fits your goals.

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter â–º https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram â–º https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook â–º https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok â–º https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-Â­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

snippet.title: Saagar Jaisi Aankhon Wali (Lyrical Video) | Kishore Kumar | R. D. Burman | Revibe | Hindi Songs
snippet.description:
Saagar Jaisi Aankhon Wali â€“ A poetic and unforgettable love song from the classic film Saagar (1985), sung by the legendary Kishore Kumar and composed by the maestro R.D. Burman. The lyrics, written by Javed Akhtar, beautifully describe the depth and beauty of a womanâ€™s eyes â€” like the vastness of the sea.

Featuring Rishi Kapoor, Kamal Haasan, and Dimple Kapadia, this romantic melody captures a moment of innocent admiration and heartfelt emotion. With its soulful composition, gentle vocals, and graceful visuals, this song remains one of Bollywoodâ€™s most cherished expressions of love.

Credits: 
Singer: Kishore Kumar
Music: R. D. Burman
Lyrics: Javed Akhtar
Movie: Saagar
Starring: Rishi Kapoor, Kamal Haasan, Dimple Kapadia
Director: Ramesh Sippy
Producer: G. P. Sippy
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics:

Chehra hai ya chand khila hai  
  
Zulf ghaneri shaam hai kya  
  
Saagar jaisi aankhon waali  
  
Yeh to bata tera naam hai kya  
  
Chehra hai ya chand khila hai  
  
Zulf ghaneri shaam hai kya  
  
Saagar jaisi aankhon waali  
  
Yeh to bata tera naam hai kya  
  
Arre tu kya jaane teri khatir  
  
Kitna hai betaab yeh dil  
  
Tu kya jaane dekh raha hai  
  
Kaise kaise khwaab yeh dil  
  
Dil kehta hai tu hai yahan to  
  
Jata lamha tham jaaye  
  
Waqt ka dariya behte behte  
  
Is manzar mein jam jaaye  
  
Tune deewana dil ko banaya  
  
Is dil pe ilzam hai kya  
  
Saagar jaisi aankhon waali  
  
Yeh to bata tera naam hai kya  
  
Ho aaj main tujhse door sahi  
  
Aur tu mujhse anjaan sahi  
  
Tera saath nahin paaoon to  
  
Khair tera armaan sahi  
  
Ho yeh armaan hain shor nahi ho  
  
Khamoshi ke mele hon  
  
Is duniya mein koi nahi ho  
  
Hum dono hi akele hon  
  
Tere sapne dekh raha hoon  
  
Aur mera ab kaam hai kya  
  
Saagar jaisi aankhon waali  
  
Yeh to bata tera naam hai kya  
  
Chehra hai ya chand khila hai  
  
Zulf ghaneri shaam hai kya  
  
Saagar jaisi aankhon waali  
  
Yeh to bata tera naam hai kya
